<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>

<p>Fragment of a simple <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> moulding, probably a <rs type="objectType">column base</rs>, broken at both ends (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.14</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.02</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.051</measure>).</p></div><div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of Text</head><p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> in two lines along the one simple fascia.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure></p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0200" exact="none">Second century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">monument</rs>, <rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
<div type="edition" lang="grc">
<head lang="en">Edition</head>
<ab><lb n="1"/><gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><orig n="unresolved"><unclear reason="damage">λ</unclear></orig> <persName type="aphrodisian"><name type="

      " reg="Μένανδρος">Μενανδρ<gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/></name></persName><lb n="2"/><gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><w lemma="σύν"><supplied reason="lost">σὺν</supplied></w>  <w lemma="ὁ"><supplied reason="lost">τῷ</supplied></w>  <w><supplied reason="lost">σπ</supplied>ειροκεφάλῳ</w>  <gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/></ab>
</div>


<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p><gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>Menandros <note place="not specified" anchored="yes">case not clear</note> <gap dim="internal" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">with its</supplied> capital<gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/></p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>Clearly the dedication of a column; probably one of the column base dedications from west portico of the East Court of the Hadrianic Baths. From north section: <xref type="iAph">1114</xref> (MiItal 8 i and ii), <xref type="iAph">1116</xref> (=Haussoullier1), <xref type="iAph">1119</xref> (=Boulanger A 73, no.11); from the south section <xref type="iAph">1115</xref> (=Boulanger B, 21 no.28), ?<xref type="iAph">1117</xref> (=Museum 154), ?<xref type="iAph">1120</xref> (=Museum 158); cf also <xref type="iAph">1118</xref> (=68.272)</p>
</div>
